## Additional Terms for Digital ShramSetu Implementation

This software is developed as part of NITI Aayog's Digital ShramSetu initiative 
to empower India's 490 million informal workers. Any commercial use of this 
software should align with the mission of financial inclusion and worker 
empowerment in India.

## Data Protection Compliance

This software implements privacy-by-design principles and complies with:
- Digital Personal Data Protection Act (DPDP) 2023, India
- W3C Verifiable Credentials standards
- ISO 27001 security standards

